metadata.name: noodlef zozozo_tan tan
metadata.description:
A Gourmet Pixie character by Noodle (Ramen) and Wolf (Wolf).
The color of the body and shoes changes depending on the ramen soup (soy sauce, salt, miso, tantanmen, and more!)
I love using kung fu shoes with donburi tights (tracksuits).
A dark weapon (hidden weapon) is topped (equipped). (Menma three-section staff, Naruto shuriken, char siu...?)
There are sharp eyes shining behind the long hair of the noodles...!?
